Interface Payable

All Known Implementing Classes:
BasePlusCommissionEmployee, CommissionEmployee, Employee, HourlyEmployee, Invoice, SalariedEmployee
public interface Payable
The Payable interface defines a contract for objects that can be paid. Classes that implement this interface must provide an implementation of the 'getPaymentAmount' method, which calculates the payment amount.

    getPaymentAmount()
